Pacman
1.)	The game shall display a maze with walls, paths, pellets, and power pellets.
2.)	The player shall control Pac-Man using directional input.
3.)	Pac-Man shall collect a pellet when moving onto a pellet tile.
4.)	The game shall increase the score when pellets are collected.
5.)	The game shall include at least one ghost that moves automatically through the maze.
6.)	The game shall remove a life if a ghost collides with Pac-Man while not frightened.
7.)	The game shall activate frightened mode when Pac-Man consumes a power pellet.
8.)	During frightened mode, Pac-Man shall be able to eat ghosts for bonus points.
9.)	The game shall end when all lives are lost.
10.) The game shall complete the level when all pellets are consumed.


